{"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/oudsthemesorange\/orangethemebuttoncomponenttokensprovider"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"A class which wraps all "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"component  tokens of buttons"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" for ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"button"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" objects like ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSButton","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":".","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"Contains also references to semantic tokens providers so as to be able to use them to define the component tokens.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"This provider should be integrated as a ","type":"text"},{"code":"AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation inside ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" so as to provide","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"all tokens to the users. It helps users to override some of the tokens and assign them to an ","type":"text"},{"code":"OUDSTheme","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" implementation to use.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"Custom themes can use subclass of ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"},{"text":" and apply the provider they need.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"It implements also the protocol "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ButtonComponentTokens"},{"type":"text","text":" so as to expose the component tokens for "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"buttons","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" through any "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"OUDSTheme"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Button"}]},{"type":"text","text":" components tokens are defined with raw and semantic tokens of sizes (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSizeSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":"), borders"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"spaces (from "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"AllSpaceSemanticTokensProvider"},{"type":"text","text":")."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange\/OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/documentation\/OUDSThemesOrange"]]},"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/AllButtonComponentTokensProvider","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent06ButtonB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/19OUDSTokensComponent010ButtonMonoB6TokensP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesOrange\/s8CopyableP","doc:\/\/OUDSThemesContract\/documentation\/OUDSThemesContract\/TokensProvider"],"title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo"}],"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"patch":0,"minor":3},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"class","roleHeading":"Class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Theme Orange"}],"title":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider","role":"symbol","externalID":"s:16OUDSThemesOrange0B34ThemeButtonComponentTokensProviderC","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OrangeThemeButtonComponentTokensProvider"}],"languages":["swift"],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Overview","level":2,"anchor":"overview","type":"heading"},{"syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Define your own provider for button component tokens","    \/